Ini struktur FastAPI minimal yang production-ready:

```python
from fastapi import FastAPI, HTTPException
from pydantic import BaseModel
from typing import Optional

app = FastAPI(title="My API", version="1.0.0")

# Schema
class Item(BaseModel):
    name: str
    price: float
    stock: Optional[int] = 0

# In-memory store (ganti dengan database di production)
items: dict[int, Item] = {}
counter = 0

@app.get("/items/{item_id}")
def get_item(item_id: int) -> Item:
    if item_id not in items:
        raise HTTPException(status_code=404, detail="Item tidak ditemukan")
    return items[item_id]

@app.post("/items", status_code=201)
def create_item(item: Item) -> dict:
    global counter
    counter += 1
    items[counter] = item
    return {"id": counter, **item.dict()}

@app.delete("/items/{item_id}")
def delete_item(item_id: int) -> dict:
    if item_id not in items:
        raise HTTPException(status_code=404, detail="Item tidak ditemukan")
    del items[item_id]
    return {"message": "Deleted"}
```

**Jalankan:**
```bash
pip install fastapi uvicorn
uvicorn main:app --reload
```

Docs otomatis tersedia di `http://localhost:8000/docs`. FastAPI generate Swagger UI dari kode — zero config.

